Step 1: PlatformIO CLEAN

Step 2: PlatformIO BUILD

Step 3: PLATFORMIO UPLOAD 
    - Use manual select for COM port
    - BEFORE pressing UPLOAD, hold down boot button on dev board and press reset then release boot button (ESP32 bootloader mode)
    - Use 115200 baud rate (ESP32 default)

Step 4: Open PlatformIO SERIAL MONITOR
    - If using older windows, press reset on dev boad once, then press any key on keyboard (keyboard interupt)